OL,3,CAn encounter with a former gang member
OL,4,Cwho has 'seen people get stabbed'
OL,6,F'Jay' speaks exclusively to Kris
OL,7,FJepson about life during and after
OL,8,Fbeing a Newcastle gang member
OL,10,FIt is just after eight in the evening
OL,11,Fand it has been raining for much of
OL,12,Fthe day.
OL,14,FThe cameraman suggests we film the
OL,15,Finterview in a tunnel under the rail
OL,16,Flines in the centre of Newcastle.
OL,18,F"It'll give us cover," he says. Cover
OL,19,Ffrom the rain - and cover for who we
OL,20,Fare about to meet.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/13
