OL,3,CAn encounter with a former gang member
OL,4,Cwho has 'seen people get stabbed'
OL,6,FIt's been a delicate negotiation to
OL,7,Fget to this point and trust has been
OL,8,Fbuilt.
OL,10,FHe greets us with a swagger, but wants
OL,11,Fto know how we will film him and, more
OL,12,Fimportantly, how we will protect his
OL,13,Fidentity. He's wearing a balaclava,
OL,14,Fshades and a winter jacket, but asks
OL,15,Fus to disguise his voice.
OL,17,FJay - not his real name -is a former
OL,18,Fgang member. He's been in and out of
OL,19,FNewcastle gangs since he was a young
OL,20,Fteenager.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
