OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F428A1720143661
OL,3,CAn encounter with a former gang member
OL,4,Cwho has 'seen people get stabbed'
OL,6,FHe pauses and then replies: "I never
OL,7,Fused it, but the situation never
OL,8,Fhappened. I've had mates who've used
OL,9,Fone. I've been there, I've seen it,
OL,10,Fy'kna... I've seen people get stabbed."
OL,12,FThe interview inevitably enters a
OL,13,Fsubject area I know I need to probe.
OL,15,FCautiously, I go on. "Are you carrying
OL,16,Fnow?"
OL,18,F"I'm not gonna to talk about that on
OL,19,Fcamera," he says.
OL,21,FI press him.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/13
