OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F428A1720143661
OL,3,CAn encounter with a former gang member
OL,4,Cwho has 'seen people get stabbed'
OL,6,F"How does that make you feel, that
OL,7,Fyou're carrying a knife that is
OL,8,Fessentially a lethal weapon? It could
OL,9,Fbe used to kill somebody."
OL,11,FHe dismisses the premise of the
OL,12,Fquestion, saying: "You don't think
OL,13,Fabout it, do you? Because, you've
OL,14,Fgotta think, if I bump into my opps
OL,15,Fand they catch me by myself and I've
OL,16,Fgot that, then I'm safe aren't I? So
OL,17,Fyou're protected."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/13
