OL,3,CAn encounter with a former gang member
OL,4,Cwho has 'seen people get stabbed'
OL,6,FI ask him what it's like to
OL,7,Fpotentially walk around with a target
OL,8,Fon his back, when he talks about
OL,9,F"opps".
OL,11,F"It's hard innit, coz you've gotta
OL,12,Fwatch your back," he says. "Every day
OL,13,Fyou walk out, you could bump into
OL,14,Fthem. It's just what it is, you've got
OL,15,Fto look over your shoulder all the
OL,16,Ftime."
OL,18,FI interject: "Is it scary?"
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/13
